<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta property="og:image" content="http://jenniferdewalt.com/images/fb_icon.png"/>
  <title>How We're Feeling | Jennifer Dewalt</title>
  <link href="/css/reset.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="/css/how_were_feeling.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <script src="http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.9.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script src="/js/socket.io.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  <script src="/js/underscore.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  <script src="/js/jscolor/jscolor.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  <script src="/js/how_were_feeling_index.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  <script src="/js/analytics.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
  <!--[if IE]>
    <script src="http://html5shiv.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/html5.js"></script>
  <![endif]-->
</head>

<body id="how_were_feeling">
  <header>
    <div id="logo"><a href="/node/how_were_feeling">How We're Feeling</a></div>
  </header>

  <div id="wrapper">
    <div id="stats_container">

      <div class="stats" id="total" data-total="<%= data.total %>">
        Total tweets: <%= data.total %>
      </div>

      <div class="stats" id="average_positive">
        Positivity Rating: Calculating
      </div>

    </div>

    <div id="last_update">
      Last Updated: Never
    </div>

    <ul>
      <% for (var index in data.keywords) {%>
        <li>
          <div data-count="<%= data.keywords[index] %>" data-keyword="<%= index %>" class="circle"></div>
          <p class="keyword" ><%= index %></p>
        </li>
      <% } %>
    </ul>
  </div>
  
  <div id="info_container">
    <p id="tab" class="show">?</p>
    <div id="info">
      <p>How We're Feeling grabs tweets in real-time looking for <br>
         one of 32 hashtags related to how the tweeter is feeling.</p>
      <p>The hashtag circles light up as new tweets come in.</p>
      <p>The total tweets are how many tweets have been received today.</p>
      <p>The positivity rating is a percentage based on how many tweets express a positive emotion.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <div id="links_container">
        <a href="/index.html" id="home">Home</a>
        <a href="http://blog.jenniferdewalt.com" id="blog">Blog</a>
    </div>
  </footer>


</body>
</html>